{"type":"message","id":"1356a72e","parentId":"0ea4366f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:18:41.997Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_8e98450c-1636-4457-8f8a-f30f3aac2585","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775791121994}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e9d78b1","parentId":"1356a72e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:19:09.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I encountered an issue with retrieving AI news summaries due to a missing Brave Search API key. The API is required for this function but seems to be optional or not available by default in the configuration.\n\nTo proceed, I need to set up the Brave Search API key either through OpenClaw's configuration (`openclaw configure --section web`) or by manually setting it in the Gateway environment as `BRAKE_API_KEY`.\n\nOnce you provide the key, I will be able to fetch and summarize the latest AI news. Please specify whether you want me to obtain this key directly or if you have access to a Brave Search API service.\n\nIn case obtaining the key isn't possible for some reason, we can explore alternative methods such as using external web search engines like Google Scholar or IEEE Xplore which may be more accessible without requiring an API token.\n"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":8189,"output":171,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775791149706}}
